T1  - Behind the Curtain of Workforce Diversity: Evidence from EEO-1 Reports
AU  - Bourveau, Thomas
AU  - Flam, Rachel W.
AU  - Le, Anthony
Y1  - 2025/10/28
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2026/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2024.07432
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.2024.07432
